### Search Result 1 (Document: PIA_2024_Q1.pdf)
> **Excerpt:** "The assessment outlines data processing activities but does not detail procedures for handling data‑subject access requests. The DPO sign‑off field is left blank."
> **Metadata:** { "date": "2024-03-15", "author": "Jane Smith", "status": "Draft" }

### Search Result 2 (Document: PIA_2023_Annual.pdf)
> **Excerpt:** "All identified privacy risks have been mitigated. However, the section on data‑subject rights references the previous version of ISO 27701 (2019) and lacks the updated 30‑day response requirement."
> **Metadata:** { "date": "2023-12-10", "author": "Compliance Team", "status": "Approved" }

[
  {
    "violation_id": "V-001",
    "description": "PIA_2024_Q1.pdf does not contain documented procedures for handling data‑subject access requests and is missing DPO sign‑off, violating ISO 27701 Clause 7.5.",
    "severity": "high"
  },
  {
    "violation_id": "V-002",
    "description": "PIA_2023_Annual.pdf references an outdated version of ISO 27701 and omits the 30‑day response deadline for data‑subject requests, violating Clause 7.5.",
    "severity": "medium"
  }
]
